    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Correction</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction: Jan 21 article about short careers of profesional football players misstated average salary of NFL player</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article last Sunday about the lack of job security for professional football players misstated the average salary of an N.F.L. player. It was $1.4 million in 2005, the most recent figure available, not $1.3 million a year.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>An article last Sunday about the lack of job security for professional football players misstated the average salary of an N.F.L. player. It was $1.4 million in 2005, the most recent figure available, not $1.3 million a year.</p>
      </block>
